# 🚀 Task Manager App (Full Stack)

A full-stack **Task Manager Application** built using **Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Vanilla JavaScript (Axios)** with **JWT Authentication**.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

* 🔗 Frontend: https://chamithkumar.github.io/taskmanager-auth-day19-20/
* 🔗 Backend: https://taskmanager-auth-day19.onrender.com
* 🔗 Netlify: https://task-manager-full-amith.netlify.app
* video: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZF1MwzvVrw3c4D_LYrwa78j6Zh1KkD3w/view?usp=drive_link

---

## 📌 Features

* ✅ User Signup & Login (JWT आधारित authentication)
* 🔐 Protected Routes (only logged-in users can access tasks)
* 📝 Add Tasks
* ✏️ Edit Tasks
* ❌ Delete Tasks
* ✔️ Mark Tasks as Completed
* 🔍 Search Tasks
* 📂 Categories (Work, Personal, Urgent)
* 🚪 Logout System

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Backend

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB (Mongoose)
* JWT (jsonwebtoken)
* bcryptjs
* dotenv
* cors

### Frontend

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* Axios

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
project/
│
├── models/
│   ├── User.js
│   └── Task.js
│
├── middleware/
│   └── auth.js
│
├── server.js
├── .env
└── package.json
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation (Local Setup)

### 1. Clone Repository

```
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git
cd your-repo-name
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```
npm install
```

### 3. Setup Environment Variables

Create `.env` file:

```
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_url
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
```

### 4. Run Server

```
node server.js
```

Server will run at:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

---

## 🔐 API Endpoints

### Auth

* POST `/signup` → Register user
* POST `/login` → Login & get token

### Tasks (Protected)

* GET `/tasks` → Get user tasks
* POST `/tasks` → Add task
* PUT `/tasks/:id` → Update task
* DELETE `/tasks/:id` → Delete task

---

## 🔑 Authentication

After login, token is stored in:

```
localStorage
```

Send token in headers:

```
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

---

## 🚀 Deployment

* Frontend → GitHub Pages
* Backend → Render
* Database → MongoDB Atlas

